Just think of EQGems as yet another feature you choose to not use.<BR>
<BR>
As to Everquest admitting anything about downtimes...game balance would be<BR>
impacted if they changed mana regen, hp regen, etc.  Game balance is not<BR>
impacted by adding a little &quot;in game&quot; feature.<BR>
<BR>
Whether or not EQGems is appropriate for EQ, that's just personal preference.<BR>
